263
00:24:15,121 --> 00:24:17,922
    Oh, there's always time
    for polite conversation.

264
00:24:17,924 --> 00:24:20,724
          At least sit down.

265
00:24:20,726 --> 00:24:22,960
        Do you know our
        Dr. Moore here?

266
00:24:22,962 --> 00:24:26,931
      We met briefly
      this morning and, yes,
      we'll visit frequently.

267
00:24:26,933 --> 00:24:28,399
  No, we won't.

268
00:24:28,401 --> 00:24:30,234
  Let me make this
