        Here you are.

274
00:24:56,095 --> 00:24:58,529
  My credentials are gone.

275
00:24:58,531 --> 00:25:00,631
      You took them.

276
00:25:00,633 --> 00:25:03,667
          Oh, Nurse Manning,
          why would I do

277
00:25:03,669 --> 00:25:05,970
        such a cruel
