344
00:32:30,649 --> 00:32:32,582
        Oh, my!

345
00:32:32,584 --> 00:32:35,319
    Your lovely things.

346
00:32:35,321 --> 00:32:37,821
        And your suit!

347
00:32:37,823 --> 00:32:39,656
      Oh, my dear,
      why did you do it?

348
00:32:39,658 --> 00:32:41,658
              I didn't do it.

349
00:32:44,163 --> 00:32:46,430
            I didn't do it!

350
00:32:46,432 --> 00:32:50,334
      The destruction of clothes
