351
00:32:50,336 --> 00:32:52,469
          And what is naked?

352
00:32:52,471 --> 00:32:55,005
              Naked is to be
              a fetus again.

353
00:32:55,007 --> 00:32:59,309
        Always back to the womb,
          to go so far back
