354
00:32:59,311 --> 00:33:01,345
  That's ridiculous.

355
00:33:01,347 --> 00:33:04,081
      Surely, you are not
      saying you didn't
      do it yourself?

356
00:33:04,083 --> 00:33:06,183
          That's exactly
          what I'm saying.

357
00:33:07,853 --> 00:33:11,421
              Who... Why would
            anyone do that here?

358
00:33:11,423 --> 00:33:13,890
  To force me to
  wear this uniform.

359
00:33:15,094 --> 00:33:17,427
            Now, my dear,
            Miss Manning,
            try and think back.

360
00:33:17,429 --> 00:33:21,431
    I did ask you if you
   objected to wearing a uniform
    and you said you didn't.

361
00:33:21,433 --> 00:33:23,700
  That was before this.

362
00:33:23,702 --> 00:33:25,869
        I repeat, it's the
        desire to be naked...

363
00:33:25,871 --> 00:33:28,772
    Etcetera, etcetera,
    Dr. Preisser. I'm sure
    you've made your point.

364
00:33:28,774 --> 00:33:30,674
        I insist!

365
00:33:30,676 --> 00:33:33,377
      The clothes represent
      a deep hatred of self!

366
00:33:33,379 --> 00:33:35,045
      This is insanity!

367
00:33:35,047 --> 00:33:39,883
        That, I'm afraid, Nurse,
        is the business at hand.

368
00:33:39,885 --> 00:33:43,553
        Dr. Moore, do you think
       that this act of violence

369
00:33:43,555 --> 00:33:47,357
          and the suicide of
          Nurse Manning's friend
          had any connection?

370
00:33:47,359 --> 00:33:50,460
      Dr. Paul Swanson is dead.

371
00:33:50,462 --> 00:33:52,629
        He is not relevant!

372
00:33:52,631 --> 00:33:55,298
          And he will not be
          given an autopsy.

373
00:33:57,136 --> 00:34:01,038
      You, gentlemen,
      dishonor your profession.

374
00:34:01,040 --> 00:34:03,974
        More than that,
        you exploit the ill.

375
00:34:38,243 --> 00:34:41,378
              May I have my
              sweet now, please?

376
00:34:41,380 --> 00:34:44,014
          (SIGHS)
          Oh, David.

377
00:34:44,016 --> 00:34:45,916
    I forgot, I'm sorry.

378
00:34:45,918 --> 00:34:49,686
    I was, uh... I was
    upset and selfish.

379
00:34:49,688 --> 00:34:52,856
            Oh, all right,
            perhaps tomorrow.

380
00:34:52,858 --> 00:34:55,058
        Thank you for
        understanding.

