387
00:35:13,245 --> 00:35:16,079
              A sweet tomorrow
              will be just fine!

388
00:35:16,081 --> 00:35:18,215
            I'll have something
            to look forward to!

389
00:35:18,217 --> 00:35:20,317
              You are very kind!

390
00:35:20,319 --> 00:35:22,786
              (GASPING)

391
00:35:22,788 --> 00:35:24,988
  Please, don't beat me!
  I did nothing!

392
00:35:24,990 --> 00:35:26,656
  She's my friend! Please!

393
00:35:26,658 --> 00:35:28,125
      (GRUNTS)

394
00:35:28,127 --> 00:35:31,394
          That will be all, Gow!
          You will not
          punish my people!

395
00:35:31,396 --> 00:35:33,063
        (COUGHS)

396
00:35:33,065 --> 00:35:34,164
                   I'll be back.

397
00:35:34,166 --> 00:35:35,665
               Shut the fuck up!

398
00:35:35,667 --> 00:35:38,468
            Stop it!
            You hear me? Stop!

399
00:35:39,104 --> 00:35:41,238
            Gow, you shit!

400
00:35:43,475 --> 00:35:46,343
            Now, we've
            discussed this,
            haven't we, David?

401
00:35:46,345 --> 00:35:48,278
        You mustn't hurt people.

402
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,346
            (WHIMPERS)

403
00:35:49,348 --> 00:35:51,882
              Do you understand?

404
00:35:54,686 --> 00:35:56,353
      You could have killed her.

405
00:35:57,923 --> 00:35:59,656
            (SOBBING)

406
00:36:26,885 --> 00:36:28,685
            You're all right.
           You're gonna be fine.

407
00:36:28,687 --> 00:36:30,887
      I'm not gonna
      be fine here.

408
00:36:30,889 --> 00:36:34,324
              What on earth
            possessed you to get
            that close to David?

409
00:36:34,326 --> 00:36:35,559
        Pity.

