411
00:36:37,896 --> 00:36:40,297
            Therapy. And you
            committed yourself.

412
00:36:42,801 --> 00:36:44,734
    You still don't believe
    I'm sane, do you?

413
00:36:44,736 --> 00:36:46,636
          I believe that
          I can help.

414
00:36:46,638 --> 00:36:50,574
        Dr. Moore,
        I am not insane.

415
00:36:50,576 --> 00:36:52,576
        I came here to work.

416
00:36:54,246 --> 00:36:56,913
      I'll make time for
      you tomorrow afternoon
      at 3:00.

417
00:36:56,915 --> 00:36:59,316
          We can talk then.

418
00:36:59,318 --> 00:37:02,819
          Rest. Now, you'll
          be all right.

419
00:37:02,821 --> 00:37:05,589
                  It'll be fine.
                  Believe me.

420
00:37:53,639 --> 00:37:55,171
                      (GASPS)
                      Hi!

421
00:37:56,408 --> 00:37:58,475
  Do you want
  some company?

422
00:38:00,712 --> 00:38:02,812
  Do you remember me?

423
00:38:04,116 --> 00:38:06,316
                          Yes.

424
00:38:06,318 --> 00:38:08,785
  You feel like
  you don't belong here.

425
00:38:08,787 --> 00:38:10,153
                      I don't.

426
00:38:11,757 --> 00:38:15,725
  That's the way
  everybody thought
  when they first came.

427
00:38:15,727 --> 00:38:19,262
  But then you...
  You'll accept.

428
00:38:19,264 --> 00:38:20,797
  You'll see.

429
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,734
  Would you like to cry?

430
00:38:24,736 --> 00:38:26,569
          Then cry.

431
00:38:27,839 --> 00:38:32,075
  I believe that crying in
  the presence of someone

432
00:38:32,077 --> 00:38:34,678
  is more comforting
  than to cry alone.

433
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:37,180
  I cried for days
  when I first came here.

434
00:38:38,850 --> 00:38:40,750
      And I cried alone.

435
00:38:41,653 --> 00:38:43,420
      You're not alone.

436
00:38:45,957 --> 00:38:48,058
      That's really nice of you.

437
00:38:50,495 --> 00:38:51,861
          What's your name?

438
00:38:51,863 --> 00:38:53,029
              Ronnie.

439
00:38:53,031 --> 00:38:54,698
                Ronnie.

440
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:56,533
          We're gonna be
          great friends,
