450
00:39:25,864 --> 00:39:28,298
        But we're gonna
        be great friends,
        aren't we?

451
00:39:30,035 --> 00:39:32,936
        Ronnie, tell me
        more about the keys.

452
00:39:35,006 --> 00:39:38,742
  They open everything.
  This one here,

453
00:39:38,744 --> 00:39:40,210
  key to my heart.

454
00:39:40,212 --> 00:39:41,978
  (LAUGHING)

